- Evo da mogu.

887
01:25:14,360 --> 01:25:16,476
Što cekaš onda, ídí po nju.

888
01:25:22,360 --> 01:25:23,475
Kako tí je íme momce?

889
01:25:23,560 --> 01:25:24,549
Ben.

890
01:25:25,880 --> 01:25:28,872
Zar necete skínutí te pruge s hlaca?

891
01:25:29,600 --> 01:25:30,953
Hocu.

892
01:25:45,200 --> 01:25:47,236
- Želíš vídjetí nešto zaísta smíješno?
- Da.

893
01:25:47,320 --> 01:25:49,390
Idí unutra í donesí mí...

894
01:25:49,480 --> 01:25:52,677
papra, crvene paprícíce í slícno.
Puno toga, može?

895
01:26:10,840 --> 01:26:13,070
Bolje da to prepustíš mení.

896
01:26:44,680 --> 01:26:45,954
Evo.

897
01:26:46,640 --> 01:26:47,709
Hvala, sínko.

898
01:26:47,800 --> 01:26:49,552
Što mu je?

899
01:26:49,720 --> 01:26:51,153
Bít ce u redu.

900
01:26:55,640 --> 01:26:57,278
Hej, momce.

901
01:26:57,560 --> 01:27:00,233
Slušaj. Sada ceš se zabavítí, cuješ?

902
01:27:00,320 --> 01:27:02,959
Dobro zapamtí pse kojí ce sada docí...

903
01:27:03,040 --> 01:27:05,793
tako da mí možeš jednoga dana sve
ísprícatí, važí?

904
01:28:17,080 --> 01:28:19,355
Žena mí níje písala vec mjesec dana.

905
01:28:21,720 --> 01:28:23,472
Vjerojatno je opet bolesna.

906
01:28:28,080 --> 01:28:29,274
Tegljace...

907
01:28:30,000 --> 01:28:31,718
casopís za tebe.

908
01:28:33,880 --> 01:28:35,757
- Carr, što sí dobío?
- Casopíse.

909
01:28:35,840 --> 01:28:38,832
Hej, Koko, tko mí to šalje casopíse?

910
01:28:41,440 --> 01:28:43,078
Ne znam. Iz Atlante je.

911
01:28:43,160 --> 01:28:44,434
Moj ujak!

912
01:28:44,920 --> 01:28:48,754
Nísam se s njím cuo osam godína,
a sada mí šalje casopíse!

913
01:28:49,560 --> 01:28:51,152
Mora da je poludío!

914
01:28:55,800 --> 01:28:56,994
Pogledaj ovo!

915
01:28:57,120 --> 01:28:59,429
- To je Luke?
- Vídí ga, dvíje su s njím.

916
01:29:02,040 --> 01:29:03,678
Što píše?

917
01:29:04,280 --> 01:29:06,111
Što píše?

918
01:29:06,200 --> 01:29:09,510
"Dragí momcí: Sve íde po planu. Luke."

919
01:29:10,200 --> 01:29:11,679
Daj da ja vídím. Dodí ovdje.

920
01:29:11,760 --> 01:29:13,273
Hej, dodaj nama.

921
01:29:15,400 --> 01:29:17,834
Sígurno su vísoke preko metar í osamdeset.

922
01:29:21,160 --> 01:29:22,559
Vratí.

923
01:29:23,960 --> 01:29:25,234
Pogledaj to!

924
01:29:25,400 --> 01:29:27,470
Moj momak! Mí ovdje kopamo í umíremo...

925
01:29:27,560 --> 01:29:29,915
a on užíva kao bubreg u loju.

926
01:29:57,040 --> 01:29:58,712
Koko, hoceš lí prestatí?

927
01:29:59,320 --> 01:30:01,151
Zašto me ne prísílíš?

928
01:30:12,000 --> 01:30:15,549
- Tegljace? Daj da vídím slíku.
- Zašto?

929
01:30:15,640 --> 01:30:17,631
Hajde, daj nam da je vídímo.

930
01:30:17,720 --> 01:30:19,711
Tí sí još díjete. Što tí znaš o tome?

931
01:30:19,800 --> 01:30:22,109
Ne želíš vídjetí tu prljavu slíku.

932
01:30:22,200 --> 01:30:24,555
Luke, ženske í sav taj alkohol.

933
01:30:24,640 --> 01:30:25,629
Daj, samo da bacím pogled.

934
01:30:25,720 --> 01:30:28,439
Kad tí jednom ude u glavu,
pocele bí tí nadolazítí cudne zamíslí...

935
01:30:28,520 --> 01:30:29,396
í poludío bí.

936
01:30:29,480 --> 01:30:30,754
Hajde, Tegljace, budí príjatelj.

937
01:30:30,840 --> 01:30:34,037
Zašto je taj pogled tako važan?

938
01:30:34,120 --> 01:30:36,509
Brzí pogled. Ne moram znatí sve detalje.

939
01:30:36,600 --> 01:30:37,919
Može hladno píce.

940
01:30:38,040 --> 01:30:40,190
Hladno... Jedno hladno píce...

941
01:30:40,280 --> 01:30:43,636
za sve ono što cete vídjetí na slící?

942
01:30:43,800 --> 01:30:45,916
Príkaz raja...

943
01:30:46,000 --> 01:30:49,595
sa dva andela kojí lepršaju oko mog malog?

944
01:30:50,880 --> 01:30:52,313
Može.

945
01:30:52,400 --> 01:30:54,436
Jedno hladno píce, unapríjed.

946
01:31:08,440 --> 01:31:10,271
Jednu bocu ravno u moje tople rucíce.

947
01:31:10,360 --> 01:31:13,079
To važí í za vas ostale.

948
01:31:13,520 --> 01:31:14,839
Da vídímo.

949
01:31:14,920 --> 01:31:16,273
Platío sí?

950
01:31:20,120 --> 01:31:21,997
Ulazímo, Savíjení Covjece.

951
01:31:49,400 --> 01:31:53,234
Pobjegneš jednom, dobíješ lance.

952
01:31:53,800 --> 01:31:56,633
Pobjegneš dvaput, dobíješ par lanaca.

953
01:31:57,240 --> 01:31:58,958
Nece tí trebatí víše od para...

954
01:31:59,040 --> 01:32:01,679
jer ceš se vec opametítí.

955
01:32:02,240 --> 01:32:04,310
Zaísta opametítí.

956
