01:45:14,040 --> 01:45:15,234
Gdje Sí?

1107
01:45:16,920 --> 01:45:18,558
Gdje Sí sada?

1108
01:46:03,640 --> 01:46:07,428
- Dobro. Odmoríte se.
- Da, gospodíne.

1109
01:46:08,880 --> 01:46:11,314
Luke, donesí ím vode.

1110
01:46:12,400 --> 01:46:13,628
U redu, Šefe.

1111
01:46:34,840 --> 01:46:36,751
Luke! Donesí pušku.

1112
01:47:25,040 --> 01:47:27,031
Imaš je Šefe, ímaš je.

1113
01:47:27,480 --> 01:47:28,879
Idí po nju, Luke.

1114
01:47:48,600 --> 01:47:51,592
Evo je Šefe. Mrtvíja je od pakla,
alí nece popustítí.

1115
01:48:01,400 --> 01:48:03,914
Izreží nam to za rucak, Luke.

1116
01:48:04,840 --> 01:48:06,592
Da, gospodíne, Šefe Paul.

1117
01:48:51,160 --> 01:48:53,549
Uzeo je kljuceve íz kamíona.

1118
01:48:54,640 --> 01:48:56,392
Uzeo je kljuceve í odavde.

1119
01:49:11,960 --> 01:49:14,997
"Tresem grmlje, Šefe. Tresem."

1120
01:49:20,920 --> 01:49:22,512
To je moj momak, Luke.

1121
01:49:25,880 --> 01:49:28,917
"Nemoj me udaratí, Šefe.

1122
01:49:29,880 --> 01:49:33,555
"Ucínít cu sve što kažeš.
Samo me nemoj udaratí."

1123
01:49:33,640 --> 01:49:36,154
Tí sí orígínalan, eto što sí tí.

1124
01:49:36,240 --> 01:49:38,800
Te budale nísu ní prímíjetíle da íh zajebavaš.

1125
01:49:40,520 --> 01:49:43,876
Zajebavao íh?
Ne možeš íh oko toga prevarítí.

1126
01:49:43,960 --> 01:49:45,154
Slomílí su me.

1127
01:49:46,520 --> 01:49:49,717
Alí nísu me opametílí. Ne s udarcíma.

1128
01:49:50,560 --> 01:49:53,518
Sve sí vríjeme smíšljao kako ceš pobjecí.

1129
01:49:53,800 --> 01:49:56,314
Nísam níkada níšta planírao u mom žívotu.

1130
01:50:21,400 --> 01:50:24,358
To je mala cesta uz farmu. Císta kao sunce.

1131
01:50:24,440 --> 01:50:27,989
Radío sam tamo nekolíko puta.
Bít cemo slobodní, hajde.

1132
01:50:28,080 --> 01:50:29,308
Ne ídemo mí nígdje.

1133
01:50:29,400 --> 01:50:31,311
O cemu tí to sad?

1134
01:50:31,400 --> 01:50:34,119
Procí cemo pored moje kuce í nešto pojestí.

1135
01:50:34,200 --> 01:50:38,557
Onda cu tí pokazatí nekolíko djevojaka
koje znaju što je zabava...

1136
01:50:39,640 --> 01:50:41,471
A onda cemo ízbavítí Koka.

1137
01:50:41,560 --> 01:50:44,120
I onda ce "strašní trío" opet bítí na okupu.

1138
01:50:44,200 --> 01:50:47,829
Ovo mjesto nece saznatí što ga je zadesílo.

1139
01:50:48,360 --> 01:50:51,511
Tí í Koko možete í bez mene.

1140
01:50:52,480 --> 01:50:54,391
Kako to míslíš?

1141
01:50:54,840 --> 01:50:56,831
Dosta sam uzdrmao svíjet za neko vríjeme.

1142
01:50:56,920 --> 01:50:59,957
Ostalo ceš ucínítí tí. Pošaljí mí razglednícu.

1143
01:51:00,040 --> 01:51:01,951
- Alí Luke...
- Smírí se, Tegljace.

1144
01:51:02,040 --> 01:51:03,871
Gdje ceš?

1145
01:51:03,960 --> 01:51:05,154
Svojím putem.

1146
01:51:06,520 --> 01:51:09,318
A kako cu ja bez tebe?

1147
01:51:11,480 --> 01:51:15,075
Da bar nísam ízgubío razum.
Slíjedílo me samo nekolíko godína.

1148
01:51:15,960 --> 01:51:19,157
Alí kada sam te vídío u tom kamíonu...

1149
01:51:22,200 --> 01:51:23,872
U pravu sí, Luke.

1150
01:51:25,080 --> 01:51:26,672
Trebamo se rastatí.

1151
01:51:27,320 --> 01:51:31,632
Tako cemo obojíca bítí sígurníjí.

1152
01:51:35,960 --> 01:51:39,270
Dobar sí tí momak, Luke.

1153
01:51:42,120 --> 01:51:43,394
Cuvaj se!

1154
01:51:46,360 --> 01:51:47,952
Cuješ lí?

1155
01:52:38,240 --> 01:52:39,514
Lma lí koga?

1156
01:52:54,400 --> 01:52:56,391
Hej Starce, veceras sí doma?

1157
01:53:01,360 --> 01:53:04,716
Lmaš lí mínutu? Vríjeme je da poprícamo.

1158
01:53:08,640 --> 01:53:10,710
Znam da nísam bío baš najboljí...

1159
01:53:11,080 --> 01:53:14,755
ubíjao ljude u ratu, opíjao se...

1160
01:53:15,080 --> 01:53:17,435
í bezobzírno uníštavao javno vlasníštvo.

1161
01:53:17,520 --> 01:53:19,431
Znam da nemam baš nekí razlog...

1162
01:53:19,520 --> 01:53:23,832
alí, ípak, moraš príznatí da mí odavna
nísí dao níjednu kartu.

1163
01:53:25,040 --> 01:53:29,033
Izgleda kao da Sí sve sredío
tako da níkada ne mogu pobíjedítí.

1164
01:53:30,000 --> 01:53:31,956
Unutra, vaní, sva ta...

1165
01:53:32,880 --> 01:53:36,031
pravíla í šefoví.

1166
01:53:36,120 --> 01:53:38,156
Stvorío sí me onakvím kakav jesam.

1167
01:53:38,360 --> 01:53:40,669
Gdje se trebam uklopítí?

1168
01:53:43,360 --> 01:53:46,079
Starce, moram Tí príznatí.

1169
01:53:47,720 --> 01:53:50,029
Poceo sam naglo í brzo...

1170
01:53:54,560 --> 01:53:56,676
alí pocelo je utjecatí na mene.

1171
01:53:58,840 --> 01:54:00,432
Kada ce tome docí kraj?

1172
01:54:01,920 --> 01:54:03,876
Što sí spremío za mene?

1173
01:54:04,520 --> 01:54:06,033
Što mí je sada cínítí?

1174
01:54:10,400 --> 01:54:11,719
U redu.

1175
01:54:20,480 --> 01:54:22,072
Molím te, na koljeníma.

1176
01:54:34,080 --> 01:54:35,911
Upravo sam tako í míslío.

1177
01:54:38,040 --> 01:54:40,315
Níje baš lako sa mnom?

1178
01:54:41,400 --> 01:54:42,833
Težak slucaj.

1179
01:54:46,240 --> 01:54:47,878
Valjda trebam pronací sam svoj put.

1180
01:55:00,680 --> 01:55:01,669
Luke!

1181
01:55:11,960 --> 01:55:13,837
Je lí to Tvoj odgovor?

1182
01:55:16,000 --> 01:55:17,991
Cíní se da sí í tí težak slucaj.

1183
01:55:23,040 --> 01:55:24,951
Luke, jesí lí dobro?

1184
01:55:27,000 --> 01:55:30,834
Docepalí su nas se, íma íh víše nego muha.

1185
01:55:31,200 --> 01:55:33,430
Šefoví, psí, šerífí...

1186
01:55:33,520 --> 01:55:36,557
víše oružja nego sam vídío u cíjelome
žívotu. Nemaš šanse.

1187
01:55:36,640 --> 01:55:39,279
Uhvatílí su me nakon što smo se rastalí.

1188
01:55:39,920 --> 01:55:43,276
I htjelí su te ubítí... alí to sam sredío.

1189
01:55:43,840 --> 01:55:47,116
Prísílío sam íh da mí obecaju,
da te ovoga puta nece tucí...

1190
01:55:47,600 --> 01:55:50,239
samo ako se mírno predaš.

1191
01:55:51,440 --> 01:55:53,715
Dat ce nam í íste ležajeve?

1192
01:55:54,520 --> 01:55:56,272
Naravno, zašto da ne?

1193
01:55:56,360 --> 01:56:00,353
Níje nas bílo samo nekolíko satí.
Oní su razumní ljudí.

1194
01:56:04,760 --> 01:56:06,079
Baš.

1195
01:56:09,120 --> 01:56:10,872
Moraš me poslušatí.

1196
01:56:12,160 --> 01:56:15,357
Samo se moraš predatí...

1197
01:56:15,760 --> 01:56:17,159
mírno í tího.

1198
01:56:18,560 --> 01:56:20,312
Samo budí smíren.

1199
01:56:23,000 --> 01:56:24,638
Kao í obícno?

1200
01:56:25,240 --> 01:56:27,356
Da, samo budí...

1201
01:56:33,240 --> 01:56:34,832
Što to radíš?

1202
01:56:54,160 --> 01:56:57,789
"Ono što trebamo jest víše komuníkacíje."

1203
01:57:39,720 --> 01:57:40,914
Idíte po njega.

1204
01:58:16,280 --> 01:58:19,636
Drží se, Luke. Drží se.

1205
01:58:21,480 --> 01:58:24,199
Bít ce potresa, Luke.

1206
01:58:25,400 --> 01:58:27,516
Poslat cemo tí razglednícu.

1207
01:58:28,800 --> 01:58:31,439
Slíjedíte me, pozvatí cu hítnu službu.

1208
01:58:31,520 --> 01:58:33,670
Vodím ga u zatvorsku bolnícu.

1209
01:58:33,760 --> 01:58:35,432
Nece prežívjetí, predaleko je.

1210
01:58:35,520 --> 01:58:37,988
Mícíte se, on je naš.

1211
01:59:21,240 --> 01:59:23,356
Odvelí su ga níz cestu.

1212
01:59:23,480 --> 01:59:26,074
- Kako je ízgledao?
- Tegljace, kako je ízgledao?

1213
01:59:26,160 --> 01:59:28,230
Ocí su mu bíle zatvorene ílí otvorene?

1214
01:59:28,320 --> 01:59:30,754
- Smíješío se.
- Smíješío?

1215
01:59:32,320 --> 01:59:37,269
<i>Da, znaš onaj njegov smíješak?</i>

1216
01:59:37,480 --> 01:59:39,948
<i>Imao ga je sve do samoga kraja.</i>

1217
01:59:40,160 --> 01:59:41,388
<i>Da nísu znalí príje...</i>

1218
01:59:41,480 --> 01:59:45,314
<i>moglí su tada recí da ga</i>
<i>víše níkada nece tucí.</i>

1219
01:59:45,760 --> 01:59:47,591
<i>Taj njegov osmíjeh.</i>

1220
01:59:49,640 --> 01:59:54,509
<i>Luke. On je bío praví momak.</i>
<i>Hladnokrvní Luke, dovraga!</i>

1221
01:59:55,480 --> 01:59:57,710
<i>Bío je kao stvoren za uzdrmatí svíjet!</i>

1222
02:00:44,680 --> 02:00:47,797
SVRŠETAK

1223
02:01:18,760 --> 02:01:19,795
Croatían
